msgid "Settings"
msgstr "设置"

msgid "Click-to-load video embeds"
msgstr "点击加载视频嵌入"

msgid "Replace YouTube embeds with local thumbnails and load the video player only after click."
msgstr "用本地缩略图替换YouTube嵌入，点击后才加载视频播放器。"

msgid "This site uses Privacy Lite Video Embeds for YouTube to display YouTube videos with a local placeholder. Before a visitor clicks a video placeholder, the visitor browser does not load the YouTube player or remote YouTube thumbnails. If the visitor chooses to play a video, the YouTube player is loaded from the privacy-enhanced youtube-nocookie.com domain and YouTube/Google may process data according to their own terms and privacy policy."
msgstr "本网站使用 Privacy Lite 视频嵌入软件（Privacy Lite Video Embeds for YouTube）来展示带有本地占位符的 YouTube 视频。访客点击视频占位符之前，访客浏览器不会加载YouTube播放器或远程YouTube缩略图。如果访客选择播放视频，YouTube 播放器会从隐私增强的 youtube-nocookie.com 域加载，YouTube 或 Google 可能会根据自身条款和隐私政策处理数据。"

msgid "Replacement scope"
msgstr "替换范围"

msgid "Consent text"
msgstr "同意书文本"

msgid "Consent message"
msgstr "内容信息"

msgid "Autoplay after click"
msgstr "点击后自动播放"

msgid "Privacy Lite Video Embeds for YouTube"
msgstr "YouTube 隐私轻量视频嵌入"

msgid "Privacy Lite Video"
msgstr "隐私轻量版视频"

msgid "Fast YouTube embeds. Nothing loads until click."
msgstr "快速上传YouTube视频。直到点击之前，什么都加载不了。"

msgid "Privacy behavior"
msgstr "隐私行为"

msgid "Before click, the frontend loads only local HTML, CSS, JavaScript and locally cached thumbnails. YouTube is loaded from youtube-nocookie.com only after the visitor clicks the placeholder."
msgstr "点击前，前端只加载本地 HTML、CSS、JavaScript 和本地缓存的缩略图。YouTube只有在访客点击占位符后才会从 youtube-nocookie.com 加载。"

msgid "To verify this, open your browser Network panel and reload a page with a YouTube embed: before the click there should be no requests to youtube.com, youtube-nocookie.com, ytimg.com, googlevideo.com, google.com or gstatic.com."
msgstr "要验证这一点，打开浏览器网络面板，重新加载带有 YouTube 嵌入的页面：点击前不应有请求 youtube.com、youtube-nocookie.com、ytimg.com、googlevideo.com、google.com 或 gstatic.com。"

msgid "Thumbnail tools"
msgstr "缩略工具"

msgid "Use these tools for existing content, troubleshooting, or after changing many YouTube embeds."
msgstr "使用这些工具进行现有内容、故障排除，或在更改大量YouTube嵌入后使用。"

msgid "Scan content and generate missing thumbnails"
msgstr "扫描内容并生成缺失的缩略图"

msgid "Scans up to %d published public posts/pages per run and downloads missing local thumbnails."
msgstr "每次运行最多扫描%d篇已发布的公开帖子/页面，并下载缺少本地缩略图的帖子。"

msgid "Clear local thumbnail cache"
msgstr "清除本地缩略图缓存"

msgid "Delete all locally cached YouTube thumbnails?"
msgstr "删除所有本地缓存的YouTube缩略图？"

msgid "Deletes locally cached thumbnail files and clears failed-download retry markers. Thumbnails will be regenerated when content is scanned, saved, or viewed."
msgstr "删除本地缓存的缩略图文件，清除下载失败的重试标记。缩略图在扫描、保存或查看内容时会重新生成。"

msgid "Only Gutenberg YouTube embed blocks"
msgstr "只有古腾堡的YouTube嵌入块"

msgid "All YouTube videos found in content"
msgstr "所有内容中的YouTube视频"

msgid "Use “All” to also replace classic oEmbeds and manually pasted YouTube iframes."
msgstr "使用“全部”来替换经典的 oEmbed 和手动粘贴的 YouTube iframe。"

msgid "Show a short privacy message inside the placeholder."
msgstr "在占位符内显示简短的隐私信息。"

msgid "Displayed only if the consent text option is enabled."
msgstr "仅在启用同意文本选项时显示。"

msgid "Start playback immediately after the user clicks the placeholder."
msgstr "用户点击占位符后立即开始播放。"

msgid "You do not have permission to run this tool."
msgstr "你没有权限运行这个工具。"

msgid "Scan complete. Posts scanned: %1$d. Videos found: %2$d. Existing thumbnails: %3$d. Generated: %4$d. Failed or unavailable: %5$d."
msgstr "扫描完成。已扫描帖子：%1$d。已找到视频：%2$d。现有缩略图：%3$d。生成：%4$d。失败或不可用：%5$d。"

msgid "Local thumbnail cache cleared. Deleted files: %d."
msgstr "本地缩略图缓存已清除。删除文件：%d。"

msgid "Support development"
msgstr "支持开发"

msgid "Buy me a coffee on Ko-fi"
msgstr "请我喝杯咖啡，在Ko-fi上"

msgid "Play video: %s"
msgstr "播放视频：%s"

msgid "Play YouTube video"
msgstr "播放YouTube视频"

msgid "The video is loaded from YouTube only after your click."
msgstr "视频只有在你点击后才会从YouTube加载。"

msgid "Play button color"
msgstr "播放按钮的颜色"

msgid "Choose the overlay play button color shown before the video is loaded."
msgstr "选择加载视频前显示的覆盖播放按钮颜色。"
